  "title": "Semantic_conditioning",
  "description": "This dataset contains neuroimaging data from a semantic conditioning task designed to investigate how contingency awareness modulates neural responses during fear conditioning. The study examines the relationship between explicit awareness of stimulus-outcome contingencies and the neural mechanisms underlying conditioned fear responses, contributing to understanding of the cognitive and neural bases of associative learning.",
